        "subject": "LU-1387 obdecho: Fix gfp_mask in echo page init.",
        "message": "LU-1387 obdecho: Fix gfp_mask in echo page init.\n\n1. In original implementation, for echo persistent page\nallocation, it use CFS_ALLOC_HIGHUSER (when > 1M) to try\nto allocate pages from high priority pool, which seems not\nright, and using CFS_ALLOC_STD should be enough here.\n\n2. Add some error console msg for echo init process.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I0e9ebc6919cd93502a3d0f5cfa80e9bdad48f48d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
